{"type": "article", "id": 4409, "title": "Tre 落地灯", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-16T08:17:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 14, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233100DLJhYn97qNRAxX80.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自以色列贝扎雷艺术与设计学院（Bezalel Academy of Arts and Design）的毕业生 Roee Magdassi 设计了一款名为「Tre」的落地灯。Roee Magdassi 设计之初提出了这样的疑问：家具可以像人类与动物一样有自己独特的性格与行为吗？为此，他为这款落地灯赋予了一个鸟的形状，并将其简化为最基本的几何形状，以适应家具的物理特性，仿佛寥寥几笔就可以勾勒出来。此外，他还为 Tre 设置了一个可以调节的木质底座，用来改变灯光的方向。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233059dQ9ijbYp6aPVzL2J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/2016060523305961wjvTr0WAUdQuRa.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1078125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052330595R3LZX0Yxu7F2h48.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233100IwLiJ3F7zDbcxUvr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.2453125\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}